        dc:description           "Figure 9. Anapistula choojaiae sp. nov., genitalia. Palp: a ventral view b dorsal view. Epigynum, cleared: c dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.07 mm (a, b); 0.06 mm (c)." , "Figure 8. Anapistula choojaiae sp. nov. female: Habitus: a ventral view b dorsal view. Epigynum: c ventral view d dorsal view, cleared. Scale bars: 0.2 mm (a, b); 0.06 mm (c); 0.03 mm (d)." , "Figure 7. Anapistula choojaiae sp. nov. male: Habitus: a ventral view b dorsal view. Palp: c ventral view. Female: Prosoma: d anterior view. Scale bars: 0.2 mm (a, b); 0.07 mm (c); 0.06 mm (d). Arrow pointing to the cheliceral teeth." ;
